  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Detailed description",
      "text": "The MikroTik Power Adapter 24HPOW is a reliable and high-performance power supply designed to provide stable power for demanding networking setups. With an input voltage range of 100–240V at 1.6A and an output of 24V at 2.5A, this adapter ensures consistent power delivery even in intensive operating conditions. It comes equipped with a standard EU plug, making it ready for immediate use. This power adapter is particularly well-suited for installations with long cable runs or multiple high-power wireless cards, where stable voltage and sufficient current are essential for optimal performance. Its durable construction and efficient design help maintain steady operation over time, reducing power losses and ensuring the reliability of your MikroTik equipment. Whether you’re powering routers, access points, or other networking devices, the MikroTik 24HPOW adapter offers a dependable solution for both home and professional environments."
    }
